DOC.brief_summary: This trial is conducted in North America. The aim of this trial is asses the long term safety and efficacy of biphasic insulin aspart 30 in Canadian subjects with type 2 diabetes who had participated in the BIAsp-1237 trial.
DOC.brief_title: Long Term Safety and Efficacy of Biphasic Insulin Aspart 30 in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes
